intro: Embark on a magical quest to collect Christmas gifts!
description:
Step into the festive world of Santa's Christmas Gift Quest, a 2D platformer bursting with holiday cheer and magical adventures! Journey through stunning, snow-covered landscapes, sparkling villages, and mysterious winter forests as you collect lost Christmas gifts. 
Watch out for mischievous NPCs determined to stop you at every turn! Dodge obstacles, outsmart enemies, and soak in the holiday spirit with every step. With its magical locations and heartwarming festive vibe, this adventure is your chance to save Christmas and spread joy to the world!
